episodes.title: Woman Born In Sex Cult Has Stepfather’s Child At 12 Years Old
episodes.description:
We speak to Ta’za, born into a sex cult where she experienced sexual abuse since the age of 4 years old at the hands of her mom and stepfather. Delivering a child at 12 years old, she is on a search to find the location of her 18-year-old daughter. While her family writes her off as “crazy,” lie detector tests & medical records say otherwise. Trappin Anonymous
